iHere's the thing: there is no inherent, inaliable rights to		gopher.black	70
iNetflix. Facebook is not a universal, precious entity that		gopher.black	70
ideserves the protection and preservation of all people. The only		gopher.black	70
ithing that fits that category is the people themselves. If		gopher.black	70
