iData collection is a simple thing. It's easy to watch tracking		gopher.black	70
ievents fire and show up in pretty graphs. It's easy to use this to		gopher.black	70
ioptimize your experiences, improve them, make the user's day		gopher.black	70
ia little easier. It's easy to look at the rosy garden that casual		gopher.black	70
ianalytics presents and see only the flowers. Just like		gopher.black	70
icapitalism's promise of innovation through financial competition,		gopher.black	70
ithe premise is beautiful on the surface. Left unchecked it will		gopher.black	70
icorrupt. That corruption will consolodate power and influence.		gopher.black	70
iThat power and influence will allocate more benefit to the few in		gopher.black	70
